APA-Like Table Style

Source: R/theme_gt_apa.R
theme_gt_apa.Rd

Style a gt table minimally with an APA-like style.

theme_gt_apa(table)

Arguments

table

A gt table

Value

A formatted gt table

Examples

library(gt)

mtcars %>%
gt() %>%
theme_gt_apa()
